;would at least make the martial artist viable as the melee ac &gt;of enemies sky rockets at higher levels and we are stuck &gt;doing minimum damage.  I am looking forward to adopting &gt;weapon use into my character however so my real question &gt;in this regards is when can we expect to see the bugs &gt;regarding our weapons be addressed?<br><br><br>We will be considering changes in the MA weapons. As for now we feel like the MA is working quite good. But we feel like we will have to add more stuff to the MA over time. We will have to balance the thing in the game.<br><br>Sorry for the inconvieniences.<br><br>-- <br><br>Aleksander S. Grøndal aka (BlueOffset)<br>Funcom Customer Service <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/urypht.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rypht</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#660000>(12/7/01 8:20:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1461.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://u2.lvcm.com/rypht/ryphtmini.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /me is utopist and wrote to Funcom..got an answer</span><hr size=1> hrmmm... note to self, don't tinker with the cut and paste job in the post window, it looks bad afterwards <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/udragonflyao.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dragonfly AO</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tiny Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#660000>(12/7/01 10:43:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1461.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> 